## Campaign Content (All Rights Reserved)

The campaign content in this repository is copyrighted and all rights are reserved:

- All files in the `entities/` directory
- All files in the `audiobooks/` directory  
- All files in the `images/` directory
- All files in the `references/` directory
- All files in the `session-recordings/` directory
- All files in the `transcripts/` directory

This content includes but is not limited to:
- Character descriptions and stories
- World-building materials
- Campaign narratives and session summaries
- Audio recordings and transcripts
- Generated images and artwork
- Reference documents and campaign guides

**This campaign content may NOT be used, copied, modified, distributed, or reproduced in any form without explicit written permission from the copyright holder.**

---

When using code from this repository, please ensure you only use the software components and not the campaign content.